ExtJson
=======

Output ExtJS 3.X friendly JSON using respond_with.

Setup
-------

In your environment.rb set "include_root_in_json" to "false" by adding the following line
ActiveRecord::Base.include_root_in_json = false

Sample Controller
------------------
class PostsController < ApplicationController

  respond_to :json
	
  def index
    @posts = Post.all
    respond_with @posts.ext_json	
  end

end

Sample Output
---------------
{"data" : [{"title" : "First Post"}, {"title" : "Second Post"}], "total":2}

